s is an inter-departmental research lab at the Cyprus University of Technology investigating the increasingly digitalised links between politicians, the media, civil society and citizens — through experimentation, Voting Advice Applications and bespoke data platforms.\n  </p>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:2rem; display:flex; gap:0.6rem; flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n    <a href=\"research.html\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Read the research →</a>\n    <a href=\"team.html\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary\">Meet the lab</a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"hero-meta\">\n    <span>fig 01 · communication flow, sampled</span>\n    <span>4 clusters · est. 2018</span>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<p class=\"section-eyebrow\">↳ Research clusters</p>\n<h2 style=\"margin:0 0 1rem; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:-0.025em;\">Four clusters, one forum.</h2>\n\n<div class=\"cluster-grid\">\n  <a class=\"cluster\" href=\"research.html#applied-political-communication\">\n    <span class=\"cluster-code\">cluster.01</span>\n    <h3 class=\"cluster-title\">Applied Political Communication</h3>\n    <p class=\"cluster-blurb\">Experimental work on how political information moves between political actors, media and citizens — including pioneering research on Voting Advice Applications.</p>\n    <span class=\"cluster-cta\">explore →</span>\n  </a>\n  <a class=\"cluster\" href=\"research.html#media-and-social-media-monitoring\">\n    <span class=\"cluster-code\">cluster.02</span>\n    <h3 class=\"cluster-title\">Media &amp; Social Media Monitoring</h3>\n    <p class=\"cluster-blurb\">Bespoke data-collection platforms that track political communication across news media and social media in real time, during election campaigns and beyond.</p>\n    <span class=\"cluster-cta\">explore →</span>\n  </a>\n  <a class=\"cluster\" href=\"research.html#public-opinion-argument-mining\">\n    <span class=\"cluster-code\">cluster.03</span>\n    <h3 class=\"cluster-title\">Public Opinion &amp; Argument Mining</h3>\n    <p class=\"cluster-blurb\">Techniques and tools for the analysis of public opinion, combining surveys with computational methods and argument mining from computational linguistics.</p>\n    <span class=\"cluster-cta\">explore →</span>\n  </a>\n  <a class=\"cluster\" href=\"research.html#digipols-forum\">\n    <span class=\"cluster-code\">cluster.04</span>\n    <h3 class=\"cluster-title\">The DigiPols Forum</h3>\n    <p class=\"cluster-blurb\">Umbrella organisation that convenes DigiPols researchers to exchange ideas, share state-of-the-art practice and set strategic direction for the lab.</p>\n    <span class=\"cluster-cta\">explore →</span>\n  </a>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"section-eyebrow\" style=\"margin-top:3rem;\">↳ Latest</p>\n<h2 style=\"margin:0 0 1rem; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:-0.025em;\">Recent highlights &amp; publications</h2>\n```\n\n::: {.grid}\n\n::: {.g-col-6}\n**Highlights →**\n\nRead the latest news, project launches and lab events.\n\n[View highlights](highlights.html){.btn .btn-outline-primary}\n:::\n\n::: {.g-col-6}\n**Publications →**\n\nPeer-reviewed papers, reports and book chapters from the lab.\n\n[View publications](publications.html){.btn .btn-outline-primary}\n:::\n\n:::\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n<section class=\"digipols-hero\">\n  <!-- Signal background: concentric beacon rings + a faint sampled waveform -->\n  <svg class=\"hero-bg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1440 720\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMaxYMid slice\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n    <defs>\n      <radialGradient id=\"beaconFade\" cx=\"0.5\" cy=\"0.5\" r=\"0.5\">\n        <stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"#2E6FE0\" stop-opacity=\"0.22\"/>\n        <stop offset=\"60%\" stop-color=\"#2E6FE0\" stop-opacity=\"0.06\"/>\n        <stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"#2E6FE0\" stop-opacity=\"0\"/>\n      </radialGradient>\n    </defs>\n    <!-- emanating rings, anchored right -->\n    <g transform=\"translate(1180 360)\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E1014\">\n      <circle r=\"80\"  stroke-width=\"1.2\" 